---
title: Sweet Chili and Maple Pork Ribs Quick Spring Salad
description: Pre-cooked pork ribs make dinner a breeze to prepare and a treat to eat! We've pared these sticky maple ribs with sweet potato rounds and a bright crisp spring salad for a tasty, filling meal the whole family will enjoy!
